column5: Has anyone crossed into Canada with hunting rifles with the non-res 909 form PRINTED out off a pc? The offices are clossed for the weekend and I can't verify if this is an acceptable method (printout)
I will answer my own question, just in case antone here is following this. I just got off the phone with the CFC and the kind lady said yes, a printed out 909 form facimily is perfectly acceptable.
